3FE8FFE0.Line5.11F5B6: Yes! Yes! With only one eye! His companion was better company...

676555F8.Line3.11F5A1: Ever since that man... infected us with nightmares. With evil.

8EE1287E.Line1.11E7B7: We have been tortured... tormented... for weeks.

E2468CE9.Line7.BAE4: This man... was he a swordsman? With a companion?
